summary: A character preset inspired by Red Sonja.
descriptionHtml:
Inspired by Red Sonja. Includes two similar nord presets and Ket'Ro, an orc preset. To install simply drop the skse folder from the zip into your data folder. During character creation (or open the console and type "showracemenu" if working with a current play through) set the character to female, click the presets tab, load preset. These are strictly body/facial presets and noting more.

Requires 
-Race Menu ( http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/? )
-Realistic Ragdolls ( http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/601/? )
-Female Facial Animations ( http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35303/? )
-CBBE ( http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/? )
-High Resolution Scars/North Born Scars ( http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/4784/? or http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49279/? )
-Lore Hairstyles ( http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/25395/? )
-Natural Eyes ( http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3589/? )

Working on follower versions of both presets.
Let me know if there are any problems with the update.
author: Tom1610
